      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Spokane Is to be boosted in an\nother way beside sending out cir\nculars telling of the great wheat\nbelt in this vicinity and beautiful\nbuildings in this city.\n\n\nThe publicity and promotion COM\nmittee of the chamber of commerce\nhas made contract for the publ\ncation of a book on scenery and\nsporting places. The book is to be\nprinted on the best of paper and\nsent to ali who inquire as to the\nscenery, fishing, hunting and other\npastimes in the vicinity of Spokane.\n\n\nSome time ago an article appear\ned in Outing telling of the game of\nthis section and hundreds of let\ntiers have been received from the\neast asking for further particulars\nNow the book. with a map of the\nmany lakes in this country, will be\nprinted and sent to inquirers."
    }
  ]
